channel.title: Breencast Outtakes
channel.description:
Hey all, longtime lurker here. Figured I'd show my appreciation for the devs in my own small way by sharing some stuff I made while messing around with a new mic. I stumbled in the middle of recording a rendition of Breen's welcome speech and decided to go a bit off record, the results struck me as funny.
Download Links on Mediafire below.

item.title: Breencast Outtakes
item.dc:creator: stapleton87
item.description:
That Guy In The Corner:

“You have been chosen or been chosen” :hmph:

Yeah, that was a total Freudian slip. I didn’t even realize I said that until I listened to it later. This is the kind of stuff you miss when you do more than one take.:fffuuu:
